response.original_title: Motu Patlu: The Secret Mission Of Motu Patlu
response.overview: Dr Dang's henchmen threaten to destroy India's greatest monuments if Dr Dang is not released from prison. Soon, Motu and Patlu decide to intervene and set out on a mission to protect the nation.
